"```sql\nSELECT drivers.forename, drivers.surname, pitStops.duration\nFROM pitStops\nJOIN races ON pitStops.raceId = races.raceId\nJOIN drivers ON pitStops.driverId = drivers.driverId\nWHERE races.year = 2011 AND races.name = 'Australian Grand Prix';\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the time each driver spent at the pit stop during the 2011 Australian Grand Prix by joining the `pitStops`, `races`, and `drivers` tables. It filters the results to only include the specified race and year."